  <dsc><c01 audience="internal" id="aspace_c5c9818b0105ace2cc46f4ad4cd979ac" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series I. Frank Family and Vineyard Materials</unittitle></did><c02 audience="internal" id="aspace_83086ca9b9056bceb3c4dbcfedf5456c" level="file"><did><unittitle>General</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="1951/2001" type="inclusive">1951-2001</unitdate><container id="aspace_b30481a1a064c9a6de167ad309785414" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_0b6d0fcfe94e1de1d6a017a1364fa6d0" parent="aspace_b30481a1a064c9a6de167ad309785414" type="folder">1</container></did><scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_1838472c53ff8702008d04e14e1ee9ed"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Correspondence, reciepts, and handwritten notes. Includes a letter from the National Catholic Welfare Conference about work placement in the United States and emigration services, 1951.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 audience="internal" id="aspace_b352640e28b81149d43d385e59295a62" level="file"><did><unittitle>Booklets and pamphlets</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="1957/2005" type="inclusive">1957-2005</unitdate><container id="aspace_76428fb35efb4496a73f31010b56be90" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_38c5a1e7dd7ba4e1210db0a89c86019c" parent="aspace_76428fb35efb4496a73f31010b56be90" type="folder">2</container></did><scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_4107179d0ba4f2cc0335ac48633fddf9"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes 2003 New York Wine Industry Workshop Proceedings booklet, excerpts from books on wineries and winemaking in the United States.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 audience="internal" id="aspace_61243580b2a636311d26aedb2f5990f4" level="file"><did><unittitle>Clippings</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="1938/2006" type="inclusive">1938-2006</unitdate><container id="aspace_cd3aa8f271bf35bad7197053a47205ed" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_df7883af349531abfa6f3276020c73f7" parent="aspace_cd3aa8f271bf35bad7197053a47205ed" type="folder">3</container><container id="aspace_e23d01f613d4f17425954c81f6cc8f90" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">16</container><container id="aspace_24649ab17b747bd7ae3867f2d1e48e5f" parent="aspace_e23d01f613d4f17425954c81f6cc8f90" type="folder">1</container></did><scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_3003e616a211bf17d5743e287068412b"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Newspaper and magazine clippings relating to Dr. Frank and Willy Frank, including obituaries. Also includes pahmphets and bulletins about plant breeding, agriculture, and viticulture in French, German, and Russian. Box 16 contains oversize and laminated magazine and newspaper clippings.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 audience="internal" id="aspace_94dc0f80d158dbed2fc1e0758013db2d" level="file"><did><unittitle>Ephemera</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="1944/2003" type="inclusive">1944-2003</unitdate><container id="aspace_dd0550d459a0574d0b8f786e0d68d75e" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_3f0a404622ba96fde03a68032c394122" parent="aspace_dd0550d459a0574d0b8f786e0d68d75e" type="folder">4</container></did><scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_ff072199480627964c18a39c64039804"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes pamphlets, hunting and fishing licences, and advertising materials. Many of the materials were pulled out of books from the Dr. Frank book collection at Geneva.</p></scopecontent></c02><c02 audience="internal" id="aspace_8e40d7becde7f3aa28376aa84f15fda9" level="file"><did><unittitle>Fancy Food Show materials</unittitle><unitdate certainty="approximate" datechar="creation" normal="2002/2002">2002</unitdate><container id="aspace_a8a26fd32f5f8b9595742c9abe899295" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_50036244a77cff1a